pick <- function(df,
                 contracts=c(),
                 address_remove=NULL,
                 address_subtract=NULL,
                 address_max=Inf,

  df_by_address <- df %>%
    dplyr::group_by(address) %>%
    dplyr::summarise(
      balance = ifelse(sum(balance) <= address_max, sum(balance), address_max)
    )

    dplyr::select(address, balance) %>%

  }
}

tally <- function(x) {
